Trace the computation step by step:

    mov x1, #100         x1 = 100
    mov x2, #37          x2 = 37
    mov x3, #15          x3 = 15

    sub x0, x1, x2       x0 = 100 - 37 = 63    ✓

    add x0, x0, x2       x0 = 63 + 37 = 100    ✗  (wrong register!)

The final ADD should use x3 (which holds 15), not x2 (which holds 37):

    add x0, x0, x3       x0 = 63 + 15 = 78     ✓
